spec_data.Name: texlive-papermas
spec_data.Description:
The package computes the number of sheets of paper used by, and
hence the mass of a document. This is useful (for example) when
calculating postal charges.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:26:37 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Compute the mass of a printed version of a document
